    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a parts car or a major project for an experienced mechanic. The transmission is currently slipping significantly, and there are multiple fluid leaks under the engine bay. Body-wise, there is extensive rust along the rocker panels and several large dents on the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. Sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 3800.0,
